# Modus Icons Usage Rules

## üéØ Core Principle: Use Valid Icon Names Only

**Always use valid Modus icon names.** Only the icons defined in the `ModusIconName` type are guaranteed to render properly. Invalid icon names will not display correctly.

## üöÄ Icon Implementation Patterns

### ‚úÖ Preferred: Use ModusIcon Component

```vue
