<i class="fa fa-star"></i>
<!-- Font Awesome -->
<i class="material-icons">star</i>
<!-- Material Icons -->
```

### ‚ùå Don't Hardcode Colors

```vue
<!-- WRONG: Hardcoded colors -->
<ModusIcon name="star" color="#ff0000" />
<i class="modus-icons" style="color: blue">star</i>

<!-- CORRECT: Use Modus color variables -->
<ModusIcon name="star" color="var(--modus-wc-color-error)" />
```

### ‚ùå Don't Forget Accessibility

```vue
<!-- WRONG: Missing aria-label for functional icon -->
<modus-wc-button shape="circle">
  <i class="modus-icons">delete</i>
</modus-wc-button>

<!-- CORRECT: Include aria-label -->
<modus-wc-button shape="circle" aria-label="Delete item">
  <i class="modus-icons">delete</i>
</modus-wc-button>
```

